claim.claim-text:
An electronic device (100) comprising:
a switch (750) with

a set of bus inputs electrically (764, 774, 784) coupled to at least a portion of:
a first set of conductors (764) compatible with a High-Definition Multimedia Interface (HDMI) interface;
a second set of conductors (784) compatible with an Universal Serial Bus (USB) version 3.0 interface; and
a third set of conductors (774) compatible with a Peripheral Component Interconnect Express (PCIe) interface;
a bus output with a fourth set of conductors (790);

a control input (752, 754) configured to receive a control signal to selectively couple one of the first set of conductors, the second set of conductors, and the third set of conductors to the fourth set of conductors of the bus output; and

a HDMI compatible (720) connector with HDMI conductors, and at least a portion of the HDMI conductors electrically coupled to the bus output.
